	<ThingDef ParentName="GW_TotE_ArmorBase">
		<defName>GW_TotE_AllarusArmor</defName>
		<label>allarus armor</label>
        <description>A suit of Terminator Power Armor, crafted from auramite for the Allarus Custodians of the Adeptus Custodes. Stronger even than their ceramite cousins, the protection provided by this armor exceeds that of some armored vehicles.\n\nAllarus Terminators are tasked with exterminating high-value targets in the field. Such is their relentlessness that the Allarus Terminator armor used to contain short-range teleporters for pursuing their foes - unfortunately, that technology is now lost to time, as is that of their wrist-mounted Balistus Grenade Launchers.</description>
